    "is_free": false,
    "description": "这是一款故事驱动的生存恐怖游戏，讲述了 90 年代初发生的经典外星人入侵。作为配备棒球棒和几颗子弹的左轮手枪的瑞恩贝克，故事将带您穿越被不明飞行物和灰色外星人入侵的灰山大气社区。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1905020/extras/cca5df18f34794ac3e275cd5b0149cc8.poster.avif?t=1730376629\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1905020/extras/cca5df18f34794ac3e275cd5b0149cc8.webm?t=1730376629\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1905020/extras/cca5df18f34794ac3e275cd5b0149cc8.mp4?t=1730376629\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在美国，90 年代初，媒体谈论气象气球和阴谋论。但是这个小社区的居民很快就意识到了！<br><strong>政府在撒谎。</strong><br>过去几天最近增加的超自然活动使格雷希尔害怕和现在偏执的居民相信政府以某种方式参与其中。<br>他们不信任任何人。 Greyhill 的小社区不敢说出来，害怕被送进精神病房，不敢报警。<br>独自一人，他们通过用木板封住窗户并建立邻里守望来做好准备。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1905020/extras/2085efcae02de5d136605dc600c6e678.poster.avif?t=1730376629\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1905020/extras/2085efcae02de5d136605dc600c6e678.webm?t=1730376629\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1905020/extras/2085efcae02de5d136605dc600c6e678.mp4?t=1730376629\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>作为配备棒球棒和几颗子弹的左轮手枪的“普通人”瑞恩贝克，你的道路是穿越灰山的大气社区，以拯救陷入严重困境的邻居。寻找有用的物品，解开谜题，你会遇到其他邻居，为在入侵中生存而战，并引导瑞恩穿过街区。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1905020/extras/c03afc5f77bbe5d17f8ad44d90d5580e.poster.avif?t=1730376629\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1905020/extras/c03afc5f77bbe5d17f8ad44d90d5580e.webm?t=1730376629\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1905020/extras/c03afc5f77bbe5d17f8ad44d90d5580e.mp4?t=1730376629\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>潜入被外星人和不明飞行物入侵的大气美国社区的开阔区域。调查房屋和谷仓并寻找弹药，同时穿过村庄并揭开外星人的阴谋。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1905020/extras/6c92bc49c612333c37730e8512dd9dfb.poster.avif?t=1730376629\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1905020/extras/6c92bc49c612333c37730e8512dd9dfb.webm?t=1730376629\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1905020/extras/6c92bc49c612333c37730e8512dd9dfb.mp4?t=1730376629\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>一个不断的威胁用他们的飞碟入侵村庄。“他们”试图绑架村里的每个人，对一切进行取样，进行实验和探测人。潜行、奔跑或战斗以通过灰山并提防“灰人”。<br><br><br><strong>随时将灰山事件添加到您的愿望清单。</strong>",
